  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Academic Head",
  "description": "<p>An officially recognized Swiss School Abroad, we are a small and familiar school, embedded in a tropical landscape, away from busy roads and designed as a spacious learning oasis. About 260 children are currently attending our school, mostly from Switzerland, but also from 16 other nations. We stand for a high-quality educational offer with the aim of enabling our students to learn independently and creatively.</p><p>We have a vacancy for Academic Head starting from 1 August 2026.</p><p><br /></p><p>Your Profile:</p><p>• Strong managerial skills to lead and inspire teaching staff</p><p>• A successful track record of running an academic department</p><p>• Strong experience in pedagogical and academic development</p><p>• Leadership experience in Primary school desirable</p><p>• Experience within the Swiss school system desirable</p><p>• Very good knowledge of English, German and/or French</p><p>• Winning personality with high resilience and assertiveness</p><p><br /></p><p>Our offer:</p><p>• Management experience in a modern, safe, dynamic cosmopolitan city</p><p>• Work closely with the Principal to guarantee academic quality</p><p>• To shape a trilingual competent and professional team</p><p>• To grow professionally in a unique environment</p><p><br /></p>",
